- *Emotions*: Focused but time-pressured
- *Pain Points*: Hard to get back into context quickly
- *Opportunities*: Context switching aids, quick session modes

**Phase 3: Evening Deep Dive**
- *Touchpoint*: Desktop app
- *Actions*: Creates study materials, reviews difficult concepts
- *Emotions*: Engaged when time permits, frustrated when interrupted
